Lil 'Chris' Hardman was found hanged at his Lowestoft home on March 23 .
His friend AJ Sutton later identified the body as his body .
Coroner Peter Dean told an inquest that Mr Hardman had been fighting a long battle with depression and was determined to find a cure .
Mr Hardman shot to fame in Channel 4's Rock School after Kiss frontman Gene Simmons made him lead singer .